race.comment: DADDY COOL (3) is a talented dog who is a winner of nine races and filled a minor placing latest when second at this track (26.20). Can go on with it. ONE MORE CAKE (1) scored an upset win at big odds last time in a Grade 5 at this track (26.38). Should be in this for a long way. RUBEN RHODE (4) is new to this track but not to be underestimated.
